text.tspan: Daily new estimated infections of COVID-19, United States, Mar 1, 2020 to
Mean estimates from mathematical models of COVID-19 transmission dynamics. Forecasts generally assume policies that
maintain current mobility levels. For comparison, confirmed cases are infections that have been confirmed with a test (as
reported by the ECDC). See the Sources tab for further details on each data series.
Source: LSHTM (2020), Gu (2020), IHME (2020), ICL (2020), ECDC (2020)
Note: This chart does not show the latest projections of these models.
